You should try playing Subnautica! It's a survival horror game that takes place in an alien ocean on an alien planet. Your space ship crashed, but luckily you got into a life pod in time to make it to the planet safely without going down with the ship. Now you have to survive with the alien resources and look out for giant alien fish that can (and probably will) eat you. With many types of alien fish and plant life, and a large world to explore, you'll always be learning new things and discovering wonderous ecosystems. You'll also have many futuristic tools that you can make and use to your disposal. Can you handle what lurkes in the deep? Will you dive deep into the depths in search for answers as to why your ship crashed and how to get off this nightmarish planet? Play Subnautica to find out!
